{"tid":537123,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做gym身材曲線一問","createTime":"2018-01-22T11:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T21:32:57.000Z","uid":149098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e017c2fab332a4c962527b16dc0bcabb3e614366","tid":537123,"uid":149098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:56:21.000Z","msg":"今日係gym<br />\n當每個女仔都只係著好保守嘅sports wear<br />\n見到一個好有自信嘅香港女仔著sports bra<br />\n佢身材好係佢好瘦<br />\n背面望有S shape<br />\n但側面望佢個胸係完全嘅平<br />\n個蘿都唔大<br />\n巴打點睇<br />\n<br />\n好欣賞佢嘅自信 但我一直以為有身材係有前有後<br />\n定係時代變左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n情願唔要心口嘅脂肪都要瘦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef50887736c4b078ac39ed9bd89a4bea9e59fae5","tid":537123,"uid":59886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:58:22.000Z","msg":"Genetic"},{"pid":"9887ce0ade64bd0f76f978d9c6924494fb819d3f","tid":537123,"uid":77191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:59:43.000Z","msg":"仁愛堂？"},{"pid":"69bdd8cc16ed5aef1c3a08687ea97b316c23551f","tid":537123,"uid":149098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9887ce0ade64bd0f76f978d9c6924494fb819d3f","tid":537123,"uid":77191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:59:43.000Z","msg":"仁愛堂？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:20:11.000Z","msg":"No haha"},{"pid":"91845fe31ffce1540394f4f1a37fefb7cd0b4b96","tid":537123,"uid":68389,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T18:09:37.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過係個bra壓平左？"},{"pid":"e537a20c5fea09df6641816b0fc96ed8b6605989","tid":537123,"uid":156331,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T21:32:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}